I started this map a long time ago, put months of dedication and hard work into making the map I had thought of for so long. This map has gone through hundreds of trial and errors and reboots, and it was starting to turn into the image I had imagined; I wanted it to be perfect!

That, being said, was a while ago now. I haven't touched it in a few months now and have lost interest sadly. Recently I looked back at it and thought "Man that map would be such a waste to just let go, I should probably give it to someone's new or experienced to mapping and could finish it off with whatever they wanted."

And so it suddenly occurred to me, why not just give it out for free on here?

So I present: mg_city_alphatest9 (to be renamed)

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

I would NOT recommend putting this map on your server with a high number of players and expect everyone to have a fun time without encountering a lot of bugs, because I know they exist. This map is in ALPHA. 

Instead: play this map in Singleplayer, or play it with a friend. This submission exists for the interest of other mappers or players who like a bit of eyecandy ;)

As most minigame maps play out, choose your minigame from the vote room by pressing the green buttons underneath the titles within the time limit. The titles marked bright RED are not available because I either they weren't finished enough and hence are unplayable, or don't even exist but were planned.

The rest, well, is for you to discover. I hid a few fun things around the map  for players to find on their own. Use noclip to reach them if you prefer, I don't care.

And finally, if you're interested in finishing this map off, adding your own content, changing my own content, or even demolishing 99% of the map, i'm giving you the right to do so. It's completely up to you if you think you're up to it ;)

All I ask is that you keep Mine and SkiLLixX's name in the vote room, as well as the quotes I had drawn on the west side of the vote-room tower. They server as a thank you to everyone who has shown support for my mapping efforts.

Included is the BSP. Use VMEX and PAKRAT to extract the VMF and custom content. The map is a little more updated than what appears in the screenshots, they're a bit old :P

And as a last note, this is likely the last submission I'll be making on Gamebanana. Thanks to everyone who provided feedback, criticism and praise for all the maps I made. It was alot of fun :D

The final version of the map. Added: cubemap, fog, HDR, lightglow, props and changed the lighting. And light weight some levels and fixed bugs. Map contains up to 30 levels including passing, shop, spikes, trains, platforms. Levels can take many tries if you fall, then you go back to the beginning of the level if you miraculously dropped on a hard surface, 99999 HP will save you.

MG_BUTTONS_ROULETTE --------------------- The object of this map is to stay alive for 3 minutes. One terrorist has a set of 20 buttons randomly spread that corrospond to the glass tiles. Once he pressed the button that tile will go red and kill whoever is on it. You then get teleported back to a room where you have to choose another room to go in. If the Terrorist is fast at presseing the buttons; then he can take out around 17 tiles. If you are lucky enough to survive then feel free to shoot him in the head or slowly watch him die by pressing the button. NOTE: You have 5 seconds to leave the room with the doors in once you are teleported there. Also mp_limitteams 0 is required. Thanks Paul_Deagle (aka [SG] Paul)

mg_break-o-box_v4 Map made by ProfessorOak
Remake (mg_break-o-box_v4) made after the release of the original map (mg_break-o-box_v2)
 *********** (This map isn't a huge project, I made this remake while i've been working on mg_oaks_multigame)
Mapinformation Terrorist vs. Counter-Terrorist game. Try to take down the enemy team and win the game! Mapfeatures In the center of the map, there's a area full of breakable boxes. Try to make your way trough these boxes to reach enemy spawn! All boxes are breakable so you can easily make your own camping spots! There are 4 teleports in this map. The first 2 teleports can be found down under the orange strip on top of the pit. Those teleports can only be used once as they are easy to surf into. Teleport destination is enemy spawn. The 2 other teleports can be found on the bottom of the pit. Try to make your way trough the metal obstacles and you'll be able to teleport yourself to the enemy spawn! There's a SUPERAMMO gun spawner at each spawn. This spawner can only be used once and will spawn 2 guns (M4A1 or AK47) with each 999 bullets! (Very useful to break lots of boxes). There's a secret deagle, with a pigeon attached to it. This deagle has got 999 bullets aswell and looks very funny ingame. To get this gun, try to find the secret buttons in your own spawn! Map consists of 5 music songs. 1. Total eclipse of the heart - The Dan Band 2. Hey Good Lookin' - Hank Williams 3. Rockin' around the christmas tree - Mel and Kim 4. Candy Shop - The Dan Band 5. Born unto trouble - Red Dead Redemption soundtrack You'll need to know the secret to enable one of those songs. HINT: Bottom of the pit. Note In order not to make players teamkilling each other, there's glass beneath the boxes. This glass can be broken after 40 seconds, i've been playing this map for two years now and i've never seen any teamkilling before. Map's much fun with like 32 players, make sure players know about the teleports because this makes it even more fun! I hope you'll download this map, it's definitely worth it! Tell me if you're running this on your server. I appreaciate any feedback! ProfessorOak

This is a remake of a zombie panic source map called barrelhunters I believe. There are 3 t's vs 29 ct's. The cts are disguised in a box which blends in with the other boxes in the map and their only weapon is touching the T with the box to kill them. The T's get to find guns scattered across the map to fend off the ct boxes, but they are limited on ammo so It becomes a reverse cat n mouse game. Alota fun once it gets going.
